# Troubleshooting Notes

## PHP ZIP Extension
Dolibarr installer showed that ZIP, Intl, and openssl support were missing. I enabled each extension in XAMPP's `php.ini` by removing semicolon 
attached to each missing extension and restarted Apache.

## PHP IMAP Extension
Dolibarr showed IMAP support was missing. This was not required for the inventory/POS prototype because IMAP is mainly for email mailbox features, so I 
left it as is.

## install.lock
After installation, I created an empty `install.lock` file in the Dolibarr documents directory to prevent the installer from running again.

## TakePOS Warehouse Warning
TakePOS showed "Stock change disabled / No warehouse defined for terminal." I fixed this by assigning the GS-MAIN warehouse to the TakePOS terminal.
